{"parse":{"title":"Furious Crawdad","pageid":85834,"wikitext":{"*":"<onlyinclude>{{{{{tpl|tooltip}}}\n|mode={{{mode|}}}\n|arg={{{arg|}}}\n|icon=INV_Misc_Fish_14\n|stack=20\n|name=Furious Crawdad\n|quality=Common\n|vendor={{Cost|c=8}}\n|ilvl=60\n}}</onlyinclude>\n\n'''Furious Crawdad''' is a rare \"fish\" caught in the mountain lakes of [[Terokkar Forest]]: [[Lake Jorune]], [[Lake Ere'Noru]], and [[Blackwind Lake]]. Furious Crawdad share Highland Mixed Pools with  [[Golden Darter]]s. These lakes are only accessible by flying. \n\nIt can be cooked to {{loot|Common|Spicy Crawdad}}.\n\n== Patch changes ==\n{{Patch 2.0.1|note=Added in [[Burning Crusade]].}}\n\n==External links==\n<!-- Read http://www.wowwiki.com/WoWWiki:External_links before posting your links here.\nLinks that do not conform to the rules will be DELETED.\nRepeat violations may result in a BAN.\nHave a nice day. :) -->\n{{elinks-item|27439}}\n{{Elink|link=http://www.elsanglin.com/fish/furious_crawdad.html |site=El's Extreme Anglin' |icon=elsanglin}}\n* [http://www.elsanglin.com/catching_furious_crawdad.html Catching Furious Crawdad]\n[[Category:World of Warcraft common fished items]]\n[[Category:World of Warcraft cooking ingredient items]]"}}}